title: Eder Flag - Endura-Nylon with Vertical Stitching & Reinforced Corners - Proudly Made in the USA - Durable - Fade-Resistant - All Weather Durable Heavy Duty Open Weave
features: FLIES BEAUTIFULLY IN THE SLIGHTEST BREEZE - Crafted with durable, fast-drying 100% heavyweight 200-denier bunting.
BRIGHT, FADE-RESISTANT COLORS - Aniline-dyed for brilliant, fast colors - treated to resist fading.

VERTICAL STITCHING & REINFORCED CORNERS - Additional zigzag stitching reinforcement: 4 vertical rows on fly end & zigzag stitching on fly end corners. Flags smaller than 8’ x 12’ feature embroidered stars, 8’ x 12’ and larger flags with opaque white nylon stars with zigzag stitching throughout.
STURDY, DURABLE HEADERS WITH SOLID BRASS GROMMETS - Made with heavy-duty, white cotton-polyester blend army duck cloth and brass grommets for extra durability.
PROUDLY MADE IN THE USA - Eder Flag is a century-old, employee-owned company with a commitment to craftsmanship, quality and durability.
description: Fast-drying, flies beautifully in the slightest breeze. Aniline-died and treaded to resist fading
All headers are made with a heavy-duty, white cotton-polyester blend army duck cloth.
Solid brass #2 grommets are spaced evenly throughout the length of the header.
8' x 12' and larger flags include a heavy-duty plastic reinforcement sleeve at each grommet location.

8' x 12' and larger flags include plated steel rope thimbles. Thimbles are attached to the white rope using a triple crimped rope sleeve. The length of the rope is sewn into the header to stabilize its position and prevent bunching.
Includes additional zigzag stitching reinforcement: 4 vertical rows on fly end & zigzag stitching on fly end corners
